Which of the following color scheme changes for the UI are NOT available?
A. Field Shading
B. Notes Background
C. Visited and Unvisited Links
D. All are available
Answer: D
What is a DataPilot table?
A. table of contents in Lotus Symphony Documents
B. table in Lotus Symphony Spreadsheets that maintain the link of data to DB2 database
C. interactive table in which you can arrange, rearrange and summarize data according to
different point of view
D. reference table which you can map a symbol according to ASCII character in Symphony
Answer: C

C. Mail Merge allows you to use datasource from Microsoft Excel spreadsheets.
D. Mail Merge allows you to print, save or e-mail merged documents.
